  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4fd1",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "玛琉",
   "jp_text": "この「聞成ガンダムルート」は{00}ここで終了となります",
   "zh_text": "这条『平成高达路线』就到此结束了",
   "jp_hex": "15f005e00be52ce361f041f048fb35e00c3800f03e30f3aef395f0250000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce887e837e812ef2be8d2e9160de7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4fef",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "玛琉",
   "jp_text": "もっとも、私たちプリベンターの{00}戦いは終わったけど……",
   "zh_text": "不过、虽说我们预防者的战斗已经结束了{00}……",
   "jp_hex": "15f39a02a8f006f2b7f2d13700b91738f06a2df51f3209090000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8b8e7edefcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4ef28e7ffef3ae8b7e868e895e7ba00090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5009",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "玛琉",
   "jp_text": "…ケーム自体はまだ続けることも可能よ{00}この後も引き続きケームを楽しんでね",
   "zh_text": "……游戏本身仍可继续、之后也请继续享{00}受游戏哦",
   "jp_hex": "1509f763f702f0ea2bf13048f00241f1694500f0059c41f429e3d01df7634cf5d64d30360000",
   "zh_hex": "150909ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cde7fee7c0e83ae9d6e9adec0600e8c8ea94ea3ee91900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x502f",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "玛琉",
   "jp_text": "最後までこのルートを遊んでくれた君に{00}新しいステージも用意されているわ",
   "zh_text": "为将这条路线玩到最后的你、还准备了新{00}的关卡哦",
   "jp_hex": "15f145f02bf005fb354ce5ae4d30f0152a973400f40a17f43841f21622492f17484b0000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e84ae7b9e9d4e8d2e916e970e7d7e8c5e7fee7b4e7b802e7f7e87ae877e7baef8a00e7b4e8bbe801e919000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5053",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "玛琉",
   "jp_text": "私たちとは別にティターンズや{00}ネオ·ジオンと戦っていた…",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头、和提坦斯及新吉翁作战{00}的……",
   "jp_hex": "15a8f0063138e53434f0354300f02004f00c31b92d2ff013090000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e8328be7bbcde92e02e7d3e821e843e7c8e9cfef8ae7d9ee88ef2fef2800e7b409090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x506e",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "玛琉",
   "jp_text": "…ロンド·ベル隊との特別演習よ",
   "zh_text": "……与隆德·贝尔队进行的特别演习哦",
   "jp_hex": "1509f17a04f0f4bd3137e490e534f472450000",
   "zh_hex": "150909e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e892efd6e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6e9190000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5081",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "玛琉",
   "jp_text": "フリーバトルで「特別演習」を選ぶと{00}彼らと戦うことができるわ",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能与{00}他们交战哦",
   "jp_hex": "15f33071f3cd30e00be490e534f472e00c4ce39ae05a3100f0d531b918f0021cf017484b0000",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e83200e80ce7bbe861ef28e9190000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x50a7",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "玛琉",
   "jp_text": "ぜひ、挑戦してみてね",
   "zh_text": "请你务必去挑战看看哦",
   "jp_hex": "15f87902e42eb9232f3e2f360000",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae7b8e94fe860e7ebeae7ef28e7f6e7f6e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x50b5",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "玛琉",
   "jp_text": "…では、「SDガンダム{00}{01}{01}{01}{01}{01}GジェネレーシユンDS」",
