   "zh_hex": "15e7b6efcfefb5e7fae870ef70e7b4efb6ea22e8b2ef3c000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x573c",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "夏亚",
   "jp_text": "……そうか{00}では、ありがたく受け取っておこう",
   "zh_text": "……是吗、那我就心怀感激地收下了",
   "jp_hex": "150909f0091b00f00a02f3621efb3e2d2f1af0870000",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e80202e7b7efcce7c5e82deb03e87de9b9ef63e926ef4de7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x576d",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "吉恩士官",
   "jp_text": "では、変換パーツ全種{00}各1点ずつをお受け取りください",
   "zh_text": "那么、请收下各类变换部件各1件",
   "jp_hex": "15f00a02e537e129f4b9bbe2c100e1060ee463262e4cfd4de2bd47f083170000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e83ae92689e819e841e955ea78cce991e8190ee9910000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x63ee",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "時に宇宙世紀0079……",
   "zh_text": "时值宇宙世纪0079……",
   "jp_hex": "15aa34f0a8f695fc0709090000",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2dec48e8bee8bfe83ceb99e998e998eb79eca409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x63fe",
   "jp_len": 40,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "地球から最も遠いコロニーサイド3は、{00}地球連邦政府に対して独立戦争を挑んだ",
   "zh_text": "距离地球最远的殖民地SIDE3、向地{00}球联邦政府发动了独立战争",
   "jp_hex": "15f0101b46f929e0c517f09bf18210380200f010f01ef3a334e3df232ff2c7f0704ce42e4d2b0000",
