  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x642a",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "圧倒的な国力をもつ地球連邦に対し{00}ジオン公国は「モビルスーツ」を搭入",
   "zh_text": "面对拥有压倒性国力的地球联邦、吉翁公{00}国投入了『机动战士』",
   "jp_hex": "15f483e45533a1da4c412ef010f01e34e3df2300f00cf1ae38e00bf081e00c4cf5550000",
   "zh_hex": "15e862e7beeb35e7cbe992e848e951a1dae7b4bf95ef2ed102e7d9ee88e9a400a1e948e891e7ba0ce7e4ef30ef28a50d0000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6452",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "連邦軍を圧倒し、地球の半ばを{00}占領するというめざましい戦果を上げた",
   "zh_text": "压倒了联邦军、取得了占领半个地球这般{00}惊人的战果",
   "jp_hex": "15f01e984cf4832302f01037fe7c4c00fa4ff0f9171840e052f05217f70a4cf3f62a0000",
   "zh_hex": "15e992e848e7baef2eefaae7e002e987e80ae7baeb51ea20eadee828ef63efd3e7b9ea8000ec6defb2e7b4ef28e871000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x647a",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "だが……",
   "zh_text": "然而……",
   "jp_hex": "15f02709090000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7efe89c09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6486",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "当緒の予想に反して長期化した戦いは、{00}ジオン公国を皮併させ……",
   "zh_text": "战事出乎当初预料地长期化、令吉翁公国{00}日渐疲弊……",
   "jp_hex": "15f7a137f6a034e4d8232fff9ce0d9232ab917380200f00cf1ae4cffb7f02e09090000",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28a9afe933c4eb4fea5aeb8cbfef34eac9e9a502e94ee7d9ee88e9a4a100e98aed83ed8aee7f090900000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64ae",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "やがて連邦軍がモビルスーツの開発に{00}成功するに至り、戦局は久転した",
   "zh_text": "不久、连联邦军也成功开发出机动战士、{00}战局就此逆转",
   "jp_hex": "15f515f01e981cf08137f11e3400f188f00434e2924702fa5038ff31232a0000",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e9db02e86eef2eefaae7e0e7c0e837e9b1e7fae870efbee7e4ef30ef28ef640200ef28ea8ce7c5e7caeeb4e9c20000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64d2",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "数を頼みに攻め寛せてくる連邦軍に{00}ジオン軍は総報れとなり、",
   "zh_text": "面对仗着数量大举压上的联邦军、吉翁军{00}全线溃败、",
   "jp_hex": "15e3534ce5c03e34f925fae62ff100f01e983400f00c9838e3b5fd29f395020000",
   "zh_hex": "15e862e7beea37e86de914e851beea21e992b2e7b4ef2ed1e7e002e7d9ee88e7e000bbe916ec79e88f020000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64f6",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "各地で敗退を繰り返した",
   "zh_text": "各地接连败退",
   "jp_hex": "15f54930e4bce3e94cf28f232a0000",
   "zh_hex": "15e819ef63efcee86ee88fe8800000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x650a",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "そしてついに……",
   "zh_text": "终于……",
   "jp_hex": "15f115f0ab3409090000",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e2e8790909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x651a",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "speaker": "(narration)",
   "jp_text": "宇宙において、連邦軍の反攻作戦が{00}始まろうとしていた……",
   "zh_text": "在宇宙中、联邦军的反攻作战、即将拉开{00}序幕……",
   "jp_hex": "15f0a834f18602f01e9837e4d89ef0e41c00f27e4a18f028f01309090000",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e8bee8bfef4e02ef2eefaae7e0e7b4e87cef67ef2fef2802e855e84ae7c2e7fa00eb56ec14090900000000000000"
  }
 ]
